Logic App:
✅ Poll Inbox every 5 minutes
✅ Top 50 unread emails (configurable)
✅ Concurrency = 1
✅ All senders
✅ Extract email address only from From field
✅ Null body → proceed normally
✅ Large body → move to FailedEmails → Azure Monitor Critical
✅ Attachment > 25MB → move to FailedEmails → Azure Monitor Critical
✅ Sanitise MessageId (special chars → -)
✅ Sanitise attachment filename (special chars → -)
✅ Create staging folder → email-staging/{sanitisedMessageId}_{SendDateTimeUtc}/
✅ Upload attachments → retry 3 times → fail → Azure Monitor Critical → move to FailedEmails
✅ Send Service Bus message → retry 3 times → fail → Azure Monitor Critical → move to FailedEmails
✅ Mark email as read after successful processing
✅ No SQL dependency
