Edge cases:
✅ SQL fails after blobs moved → read DestinationContainer from blob metadata → check that container → re-insert DB
✅ Metadata update fails → retry 3 times → dead-letter
✅ Duplicate filenames → append -1, -2
✅ SendDateTime missing → default DateTime.UtcNow
✅ Duplicate MessageId → skip, complete message
✅ After successful move → delete staging folder
✅ Rollback failed → Critical Azure Monitor alert
